author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Now that the Minecraft movie is upon us, let's find out if its any good. Meanwhile John Boyega was taking talking points from 2019 by blaming Star Wars fans for his own character being ruined, and Doctor Who actors claim the show is doing the right thing by losing most of its audience. Smart. 

Join me, Nerdrotic, MauLer, Little Platoon and Ering Underwood for Open Bar 136.

title: Open Bar #137 - Minecraft Review, Jonh Boyega Backlash, Doctor Who Doubles Down
